### Create Location Request (authenticated)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/location-requests
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_ID_HERE

{
  "businessName": "Downtown Office Complex",
  "address": "123 Main St, City, State 12345",
  "locationType": "office",
  "preferredDates": ["2026-01-15", "2026-01-16", "2026-01-17"],
  "expectedFootTraffic": 150,
  "notes": "Looking for lunch trucks near our office building"
}

### Get Location Request by ID
GET http://localhost:5001/api/location-requests/:id
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_ID_HERE

### Express Interest as Food Truck
POST http://localhost:5001/api/location-requests/:id/interests
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_ID_HERE

{
  "message": "We'd love to serve your office! Our specialty is authentic tacos and we can handle high volume."
}
